CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1946, pg. 3 reads: "Acquire Degrees - Miss Marion Harris has acquired a Bachelor of Science degree from the University of Pittsburgh. She is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. John W. Harris, and is employed as Girl Reserve secretary of the Centre Avenue Branch YWCA...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marion Harris wearing dark graduation gown with light colored collar and mortar board, posed in front of leaf patterned background, in Harris Studio
